  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c615d5a79f8546d7b5124ccc69ba05e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image copyright Kuvaaja Soldeman\" data-size=\"2300x1294\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c615d5a79f8546d7b5124ccc69ba05e.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c615d5a79f8546d7b5124ccc69ba05e.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c615d5a79f8546d7b5124ccc69ba05e.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c615d5a79f8546d7b5124ccc69ba05e.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image copyright Kuvaaja Soldeman\" alt=\"Image copyright Kuvaaja Soldeman\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage copyright Kuvaaja Soldeman\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eRenovation work on \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/117733/alvar-aalto\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAlvar Aalto\u003c/a\u003e’s Finlandia Hall has been completed in time for a public opening this weekend (Jan. 4) in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/75685/helsinki\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHelsinki\u003c/a\u003e. Care for the landmark concert hall design was first handed over to Arkkitehdit NRT at the beginning of 2022 with a mandate to update the building as minimally as possible using new spatial and functional changes that can accommodate up to 400,000 visitors in the first year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c3216666692757d3c3028372c937b01.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x771\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c3216666692757d3c3028372c937b01.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c3216666692757d3c3028372c937b01.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c3216666692757d3c3028372c937b01.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c3216666692757d3c3028372c937b01.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Tuomas Uusheimo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8c/8c5a0c92631a46e5bcb9045f15ea3be4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1371\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8c/8c5a0c92631a46e5bcb9045f15ea3be4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8c/8c5a0c92631a46e5bcb9045f15ea3be4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8c/8c5a0c92631a46e5bcb9045f15ea3be4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8c/8c5a0c92631a46e5bcb9045f15ea3be4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Tuomas Uusheimo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;Aalto’s architecture was the starting point to all that we did. The main spaces were not changed a lot. We thought that we have to make big changes ‘behind the scenes’ so that it does not show much in the finalized building,\u0026#34; CEO and Partner Teemu Tuomi explains.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a6/a6ac6faa8b268fe1fac76879998042b7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x771\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a6/a6ac6faa8b268fe1fac76879998042b7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a6/a6ac6faa8b268fe1fac76879998042b7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a6/a6ac6faa8b268fe1fac76879998042b7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a6/a6ac6faa8b268fe1fac76879998042b7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Tuomas Uusheimo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/aa/aaef267f8b20e2f06648c82e5a0c5515.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x771\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/aa/aaef267f8b20e2f06648c82e5a0c5515.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/aa/aaef267f8b20e2f06648c82e5a0c5515.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/aa/aaef267f8b20e2f06648c82e5a0c5515.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/aa/aaef267f8b20e2f06648c82e5a0c5515.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Tuomas Uusheimo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eSome of the historically sensitive materials introduced through the renovations include patinated bronze and red beech ceramic tiles. In addition to some much-needed technology upgrades in the main hall, the new program adds dining and shopping spaces plus a two-unit residential component that offers fans of the Finnish master an overnight stay in which they can experience his architecture firsthand. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4b/4b36a7b17829d5143f3d461dbf046846.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x686\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4b/4b36a7b17829d5143f3d461dbf046846.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4b/4b36a7b17829d5143f3d461dbf046846.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4b/4b36a7b17829d5143f3d461dbf046846.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4b/4b36a7b17829d5143f3d461dbf046846.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage copyright Ville Heiskanen\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e8/e8e62e7a02419882ca628276df2b940b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x771\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e8/e8e62e7a02419882ca628276df2b940b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e8/e8e62e7a02419882ca628276df2b940b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e8/e8e62e7a02419882ca628276df2b940b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e8/e8e62e7a02419882ca628276df2b940b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto: Tuomas Uusheimo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe original facade panels on its exterior were restored, and an exhibition space was added to previously used as rehearsal areas. \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/548318/skanska\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSkanska\u003c/a\u003e provided additional help to modernize the building\u0026#39;s mechanical services, HVAC, and other services to afford a more energy-efficient operation for its next phase of life. Its more than 3,000 original lighting fixtures were also preserved as part of the renovation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/31/319f6f9243465039b9671d1d150b1e0b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/31/319f6f9243465039b9671d1d150b1e0b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/31/319f6f9243465039b9671d1d150b1e0b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/31/319f6f9243465039b9671d1d150b1e0b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/31/319f6f9243465039b9671d1d150b1e0b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage copyright Kuvaaja Soldeman\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/48/489c6c57efc0e30682ad3986348ebeef.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x638\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/48/489c6c57efc0e30682ad3986348ebeef.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/48/489c6c57efc0e30682ad3986348ebeef.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/48/489c6c57efc0e30682ad3986348ebeef.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/48/489c6c57efc0e30682ad3986348ebeef.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage copyright Satu Mali\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe project provided a unique opportunity and follow-up to Arkkitehdit NRT’s 2017 \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/bustler/6024/renovated-alvar-aalto-learning-center-wins-the-2017-finlandia-prize-for-architecture\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFinlandia Prize-winning restoration\u003c/a\u003e of Aalto’s Harald Herlin Learning Centre in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/311050/espoo\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eEspoo\u003c/a\u003e. The building was originally completed in December of 1971. A new permanent exhibition on the life and architecture of Aalto and his wives Aino and Elissa will debut inside Finlandia Hall later this June. \u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cbr clear=\"all\"/\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"comments\" id=\"CommentsAnchor\"\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/li\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/ul\u003e\n\t  \t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
